Sentencas: Oxide based two phase composite electrolyte (Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-Y2O3) was synthesized by coprecipitation method.
Titulo: GDC-Y2O3 Oxide Based Two Phase Nanocomposite Electrolyte

Sentencas: The nanocomposite electrolyte showed the significant performance of power density 785 mW cm(-2) and higher conductivities at relatively low temperature 550 degrees C. Ionic conductivities were measured with ac impedance spectroscopy and four-probe dc method.
Titulo: GDC-Y2O3 Oxide Based Two Phase Nanocomposite Electrolyte

Sentencas: The structural and morphological properties of the prepared electrolyte were investigated by scanning electron microscope (SEM).
Titulo: GDC-Y2O3 Oxide Based Two Phase Nanocomposite Electrolyte

Sentencas: The thermal stability was determined with differential scanning calorimetry.
Titulo: GDC-Y2O3 Oxide Based Two Phase Nanocomposite Electrolyte

Sentencas: The particle size that was calculated with Scherrer formula, 15-20 nm, is in a good agreement with the SEM and X-ray diffraction results.
Titulo: GDC-Y2O3 Oxide Based Two Phase Nanocomposite Electrolyte

Sentencas: The purpose of this study is to introduce the functional nanocomposite materials for advanced fuel cell technology to meet the challenges of solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: GDC-Y2O3 Oxide Based Two Phase Nanocomposite Electrolyte
